        <p>Because our Site hosts a large number of items contributed by third parties, including our users, it is not possible for us to be aware of the contents of each item or to review each item before it is posted to our Site.   Accordingly, we operate on a "Notice and Takedown" basis.</p>
<p>If you consider any material on our site to be illegal or unacceptable and wish to complain, please send us a notice (a "Notice") by email to: <a href="mailto:legal@yogaclicks.com">legal@yogaclicks.com</a> containing the following information:</p>
<ul>
<li>Your and (if applicable) your company's full name, address, telephone number and contact email address.</li>
<li>A detailed description of the nature of your complaint (such as infringement of intellectual property rights, defamation, criminal offences, breach of privacy rights etc) quoting the content in full.</li>
<li>Where the Notice relates to infringement of copyright or other intellectual property (IPR), a detailed description of the material in respect of which you claim that the IPR has been infringed and a statement that either you are the owner of, or are duly authorised by the owner of, such IPR.</li>
